com.github.robtimus.obfuscation.annotation

Interface StringRepresentationProvider

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    StringRepresentationProvider.BooleanArrayToString, StringRepresentationProvider.ByteArrayToString, StringRepresentationProvider.CharArrayToString, StringRepresentationProvider.DoubleArrayToString, StringRepresentationProvider.FloatArrayToString, StringRepresentationProvider.IntArrayToString, StringRepresentationProvider.LongArrayToString, StringRepresentationProvider.ObjectArrayDeepToString, StringRepresentationProvider.ObjectArrayToString, StringRepresentationProvider.ShortArrayToString, StringRepresentationProvider.ToString, StringRepresentationProvider.TypeSpecific

    public interface StringRepresentationProvider
    A provider for string representations, that can be used with Obfuscator.obfuscateObject(Object, Supplier).
    Author:
    Rob Spoor
